The horrific discovery of a baby girl’s decomposed body on the roof of a garage at a flat building complex in the Point area, was made on Sunday.KZN police spokesperson, Colonel Thembeka Mbele, said that Point SAPS are investigating a concealment of birth case, after a baby’s decomposed body was found on Sunday, 26 January  on the roof of a garage at a block of flats in the Point area.” She said no arrests have been made and the investigation continues. Speculation is rife that the baby was thrown from a flat in the building.